QuestData.Title: Sunken Foes
QuestData.Description: The Tidemistress... is filling her ranks with hulking naga... and sea giants.$B$BJandvik cannot withstand... their combined might.$B$BSlaughter them... before they reach its shores...
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 6 Sashj'tar Overseers and 6 Trenchwalker Scavengers in Azuregale Bay.
QuestData.RewardText: The Sashj'tar forces are far greater than I imagined.
